  <bioghist id="aspace_5f6630fdba6439e886bde41b1d7061c8">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>The Medical Society of the County of Monroe was formed in 1821.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_6e5f330a2f821e66736553ca3a908b1f">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Subject files of committees, minutes of meetings, reports, records of death associated with pregnancy and childbirth, constitution and bylaws as amended June 1876, financial records, pamphlets, and scrapbooks of the Medical Society of the County of Monroe, Inc.</p>  </scopecontent>
